<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<!--<h4>First Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti samaramukhānēka ri 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>pudarppamarddana bhujabala 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>parākrama parama maha(māhē)śvara para<note n="179-1">Inserted above the line.</note>
<lb n="4" break="no"/>mabhaṭṭāraka mahārājādhirāja 
<lb n="5"/>rājaparamēśvara gaṁggānvayāva 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>laṁbanastaṁbha śrīmadanaṁ 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ttavarmmadēvara pravarddhamāna vija 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>yarājya saṁvatsaraṁbulu 
<lb n="9"/>21(71?) śrāhi nuttarāyana(ṇa) saṁkrāṁ 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ttināṇḍu guḍivāḍa gōkarnē(rṇnē)śvara 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>dēvaraku guḍivāḍa <unclear>je</unclear>ddamanā 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>yakuṇḍu dana yuri bhukti ya 
<lb n="13" break="no"/>yina gaṇḍudēvaraku namudu 
</p>

<!--<h4>Second Face (Figures of <hi rend="italic">linga</hi> and two lamp-stands on either side).</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="14" break="no"/>naku dārapōci(dhārapōsi) yiccinā 
<lb n="15" break="no"/>ṇḍu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> dīni vi<unclear>ghna</unclear>mu sē 
<lb n="16" break="no"/>sinavāru gaṁggakaṟuta 
<lb n="17" break="no"/>vēyiṁ gavilalaṁ boḍici 
<lb n="18" break="no"/>navāru <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> bānarāsi(vāraṇāsi) vracci 
<lb n="19" break="no"/>na pāpamunaṁ bōyi 
<lb n="20" break="no"/>navāru <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
</p>

